data.description: Welcome to a home that combines classic charm with modern elegance. As you step through the front door, you’re greeted by a spacious family room, when you move into the living room a natural fireplace serves as the focal point, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  Moving further into the home, you’ll find a beautifully remodeled kitchen. The pristine white shaker cabinets offer ample storage space, while the black granite countertops provide a striking contrast, creating a sleek, contemporary aesthetic. Whether you’re a seasoned chef or a culinary novice, this kitchen is sure to inspire your home-cooked meals.  The home’s 1,511 square feet of living space is spread out over a single story, making it easily accessible. The two bathrooms have been meticulously maintained, ensuring a comfortable and convenient living experience.  The home sits on a generous 0.32-acre lot, providing plenty of outdoor space for relaxation or recreation. This home has stood the test of time, offering a blend of historical charm and modern amenities.  Come rub your feet on the fresh new carpet or enjoy the beauty of the refinished original hardwood floors. These updates, along with the home’s other features, create a living space that is both stylish and comfortable.  This home is more than just a house; it’s a lifestyle. It’s the feeling of warmth from the fireplace on a chilly evening. It’s the satisfaction of preparing a meal in a kitchen that’s both beautiful and functional. It’s the comfort of plush carpet underfoot and the elegance of refinished hardwood. It’s the peace of mind that comes with knowing you’re living in a home that’s been cared for and updated with attention to detail. Welcome to 25800 Acacia St - your new home awaits.
